{"thig6.7:0.1":"Therigatha 6.7 ","thig6.7:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.7:0.3":"Guttatherigatha ","thig6.7:1.1":"“Gutte yadattham pabbajja, ","thig6.7:1.2":"hitva puttam vasum piyam; ","thig6.7:1.3":"Tameva anubruhehi, ","thig6.7:1.4":"ma cittassa vasam gami. ","thig6.7:2.1":"Cittena vancita satta, ","thig6.7:2.2":"marassa visaye rata; ","thig6.7:2.3":"Anekajatisamsaram, ","thig6.7:2.4":"sandhavanti aviddasu. ","thig6.7:3.1":"Kamacchandanca byapadam, ","thig6.7:3.2":"sakkayaditthimeva ca; ","thig6.7:3.3":"Silabbataparamasam, ","thig6.7:3.4":"vicikicchanca pancamam. ","thig6.7:4.1":"Samyojanani etani, ","thig6.7:4.2":"pajahitvana bhikkhuni; ","thig6.7:4.3":"Orambhagamaniyani, ","thig6.7:4.4":"nayidam punarehisi. ","thig6.7:5.1":"Ragam manam avijjanca, ","thig6.7:5.2":"uddhaccanca vivajjiya; ","thig6.7:5.3":"Samyojanani chetvana, ","thig6.7:5.4":"dukkhassantam karissasi. ","thig6.7:6.1":"Khepetva jatisamsaram, ","thig6.7:6.2":"parinnaya punabbhavam; ","thig6.7:6.3":"Dittheva dhamme nicchata, ","thig6.7:6.4":"upasanta carissati”ti. ","thig6.7:7.1":"… Gutta theri …. "}